description.de:
Von dem Ersteller von be***l***iebten Ser***i***en wie ***T***wo Pi***e***ce, Da***r***uto und Detergent kommt die Serie Test, eine preisgekrönte rom***a***ntische Komödie über einen Highschoo***l***-Waffenmeister namens Yugi, der die ganze We***l***t bereist und alle Life Notes sammelt, damit er eines Tages die Leiche seines Bruders bergen kann, nachdem er das Taboo erfüllt hat, den Titan, den wir an dem Tag mit seinem Stand gesehen haben, zu one-punchen und zum Nokage-Piratenkönig zu werden -datteba***y***o. Schauen Sie zu, wie er mit seinem Onii-Chan und generischen ***H***arem Mädchen durch das He***i***lige Reich von Bri***t***annia streift, während sie alle Widrigkeiten mit der Kraft der Freundschaft, ***L***iebe und... (warum knall***e***n sie sich nicht einfach gegenseitig.) In diesem Epos in Spielfilmlänge, was das von Gilgamesch und der Ilias konku***r***riert, werden wir die Mentalität und Soziologie dieser gesellschaftlichen Bedrohungen erforschen, während sie die Erde in ihrem nie stillbaren Durst nach Imoutos verwüsten.

Rezensenten geben dieser Serie eine 10/10 für die unkonventionelle Darstellung des Magical Girl Genre.
Nominiert für die 1. MangaDex Auszeichnungen für den schlechtesten Manga des Jahres.
Gewinner der 2. MangaDex Auszeichnungen für den besten Manga des Jahres.
Der beste Manga aller Zeiten, wie Meichiro Noda feststellte.

---

**Hinweis:** Bitte fügen Sie *KEINE* Genre hinzu, oder der Test Manga wird die Suche verschmutzen. Weil dieser Manga die reinste Form aller Manga ist [Der Plural von Manga ist Manga].

**Fun fact:** Im Jahr 127, als dieser Manga ursprünglich veröffentlicht wurde, hieß er "Taest", aber wurde wegen den amerikanischen Druckkosten pro Buchstabe zu "Test" verkürzt.

description.en:
From the creator of popu***l***ar ser***i***es like ***T***wo Pi***e***ce, Da***r***uto, ***a***nd Detergent, comes the series Test, an award winning romantic comedy about a high schoo***l*** weapon meister named Yugi as he trave***l***s the entire world collecting all the Life Notes, so that one da***y*** ***h***e can recover h***i***s bro***t***her's body after performing the taboo of one punching the Titan we saw that day with his Stand and becoming the Nokage Pirate King -dattebayo. Watch as he roams through the Ho***l***y ***E***mpi***r***e of Britannia with his Onii-chan and generic harem girls as they conquer all odds with the power of friendship, love and…(why don't they just bang each other.) In this feature length epic rivaling that of Gilgamesh and the Iliad we will explore the mentality and sociology of these societal menaces as they ravage the Earth in their never quenchable thirst for imoutos.  

Reviewers gives this series a 10/10 for the unconventional portrayal of the magical girl genre.  
Nominated for the 1st Mangadex Award for Worst Manga of the Year.  
Winner of the 2nd Mangadex Awards for Best Manga of the Year.  
Best manga ever written, as stated by meichiro noda  

---
**Note:** Please do *NOT* add genres or Test will pollute genre searches. Because this manga is the most purest form of any manga [The plural of manga is manga]  
  
**Fun fact:** In the year 127, when this manga was originally released, it used to be called Taest, but because of American per/letter printing costs it was shortened to Test.  

---

Unable to sleep or find true satisfaction in his daily life, Yamori Kou begins wandering the night streets. He encounters a strange girl who offers to help soothe his insomnia by sleeping beside him, but it is not merely a one-way exchange…
description.fr: Incapable de trouver le sommeil ni d'être pleinement satisfait de son quotidien‚ Yamori Kou commence à errer de nuit dans les rues. Il fait la rencontre d'une étrange fille qui l'aidera à calmer ses insomnies en dormant à ses côtés‚ mais ce ne sera pas un simple échange unilatéral…
description.ja: 恋と青春は、夜に生まれる＿＿さあ、たのしい夜ふかしの時間だ！不眠が続く中２・夜守コウは、初めて一人外に出た夜、美しい吸血鬼・七草ナズナと出会う。「今日に満足できるまで、夜ふかししてみろよ。少年」彼女との二人きりの夜ふかしがコウの運命を大きく変えていく＿＿「これは、僕が、七草ナズナに恋をするための物語だ」眠れない夜を過ごす全ての人へ贈る＿＿真夜中のボーイ・ミーツ・ガール！連載開始から超絶大反響！！ふたり　たのし　よふかし　ラブストーリー開幕！！
description.ru: Не в состоянии заснуть или найти что-то позитивное в своей жизни, Ямори Кой начинает бродить по ночному городу, где он встречает странную девушку, которая предлагает ему свою помощь в борьбе с бессонницей путем сна рядом с ним.
description.uk: Позбавлений можливості спати, не задоволений своїм повсякденним життям, Ко Яморі перестає ходити до школи та береться поночі блукати вулицями. Там він зустрічає дівчину, на ім’я Надзуна Нанакуса, котра надає життю Ко нову сутність; укусом у шию і наступним перетворенням його на вампіра.
description.es-la: Incapaz de dormir o encontrar satisfacción en su vida diaria, Yamori Kou comienza a explorar la ciudad por la noche, donde conoce a una extraña chica que le ofrece ayudarle con su insomnio durmiendo a su lado.

description.en: The beginning of XVII century, Polish-Lithuanian Commonwealth. After the death of father, the Wielecki's family inherited a debt. Lech as the only male heir is trying to pay the charges and reclaim lost lands. To pay off the debt he is joining to another military campain.

description.en:
Zagan is feared as an evil mage, he is awkward and has a sharp tongue, and once again had to put down thieves that encroached on his territory when he was researching that morning. In a dark auction, he finds a white slave elf, Nephie, who holds a peerless beauty. Falling in love with her at first sight, he uses his fortune to buy her, but as poor as he is socially, he doesn’t understand how to connect with her. Thus, the clumsy cohabitation of the mage that can’t convey his love, and the slave that pines for her master but doesn’t understand how to bring it up, begins.  

---

description.fr:
Zagan est craint comme mage démoniaque, un jour au marché noir il rencontre une esclave elfe du nom de Nephie. De part sa beauté innocente, il tombe sous son charme et décide de l'acheter. Bien que fortuné d'argent, ses compétences sociales ne le sont pas et il a du mal à savoir comment créer une relation…  
  
C'est parti pour une cohabitation maladroite entre ce maître qui ne sait montrer son amour et cette esclave qui en pince pour lui sans savoir quoi faire.
description.pt: Zagan é temido como um mago do mal, ele é desajeitado e tem uma língua afiada, e mais uma vez teve que acabar com ladrões que invadiram seu território quando ele estava pesquisando naquela manhã. Em um leilão clandestino, ele encontra uma elfa branco, Nephie, que possui uma beleza incomparável e estava sendo vendida como uma escrava. Apaixonando-se por ela à primeira vista, ele usa sua fortuna para comprá-la, mas sendo horrível socialmente, ele não entende como se conectar com ela. Assim, a desajeitada coabitação do mago que não pode transmitir seu amor, e a escrava que anseia por seu mestre, mas não sabe como agira, começa.

description.en:
Broke young man + chainsaw dog demon = Chainsaw Man!  
  
The name says it all! Denji's life of poverty is changed forever when he merges with his pet chainsaw dog, Pochita! Now he's living in the big city and an official Devil Hunter. But he's got a lot to learn about his new job and chainsaw powers!

description.en:
Chang Xiaoyun, a policewoman, accidentally traveled to ancient times and was reincarnated as a newborn baby.
More than that, this baby is not ordinary. Her father is an invincible general. She was arranged to marry Shu Wang, the unfavored fifth son of the Emperor.
But he wants to get rid of her! …Let’s see how the heroine uses her adult mind inside a child’s body to survive and become a "pet" of the group!!!!
(from MangaUpdates)

Yoo-chan is a young man who can't get over his boyfriend from high school, who was his first love. Ever since Yoo-chan dated people that resembled his ex, but every time the relationship failed. When Yoo-chan spends a night with Namhyun, whom he thought opposite of his ex, he gets a surprise!  
  
(Source: INKR Comics)

"If you can't kiss your first love, you're dead!" Joo Dooyoon has no will to live because of his infirmity since childhood. One day, a devil suddenly appeared. It said that if you fail to meet the terms of the contract, you will die. And the condition is to kiss your first love…!

description.en:
At the age of 78, Midran, an archmage is still searching for a way to reach 8th circle. Then he is suddenly turned into a child. Will he be able to recover mana from his past life and become the Archmage of the 9th circle? This is the story of the archmage's struggle in the Murim…

Jhonny es un criminal que no fue condenado, por lo que decidió pasar la hoja y comenzar negocios 100% legales. Sin embargo su pasado no solo se opondrá en mantener su estabilidad sino que toda su vida podría desmoronarse si él se permite enamorarse de la persona equivocada.
